<item>
            <title>[PIG-2040] Move classloader from QueryParserDriver to PigContext</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2040</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1775&quot; title=&quot;Removal of old logical plan&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-1775&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-1775&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, mapreduce mode fail. The reason is we move classloader from LogicalPlanBuilder to QueryParserDriver, which will need antlr.jar, however, we don&apos;t ship antlr.jar to backend. It is better to move classloader to PigContext.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12506230">PIG-2040</key>
            <summary>Move classloader from QueryParserDriver to PigContext</summary>
